<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">HI</font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="color: #1f497d"><font face="Calibri">Send the best matching resumes ASAP</font></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Direct Client req</span></strong></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Process &amp; Product Quality Analyst</span></strong></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Location: </span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Raleigh,&nbsp;NC&nbsp;,USA</span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt; text-shadow: auto">Duration: 6+ months</span></strong></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: #1f497d; font-size: 10pt; text-shadow: auto">Reply with expected rate.</span></strong></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Requirements: </span></div>
<div style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 10pt">&middot;<span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Degree, Computer Science or related field preferred. </span></div>
<div style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 10pt">&middot;<span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Suitable candidates should also possess demonstrable proficiency with either SQL Server or Oracle programming languages (T-SQL or PL/SQL) </span></div>
<div style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 10pt">&middot;<span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">QA experience with a passion for QA and for applying your technical skills to the practice of QA. Experience with QA automation tools and performance testing tools is a plus. Infrastructure / hardware architecture experience is desired. </span></div>
<div style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 10pt">&middot;<span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Must have experience working on small and midsize projects </span></div>
<div style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 10pt">&middot;<span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Must have experience working with single product/multiple platforms</span></div>
<div style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 10pt">&middot;<span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Ability to work effectively both independently and in a small team environment </span></div>
<div style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 10pt">&middot;<span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Strong time management skills and multitasking abilities </span></div>
<div style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; text-shadow: auto">&middot;<span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 10pt">Good oral, written and presentation skills Services-Migration Practice Overview Migrations Practice is a team of consulting professionals who assist our clients with major upgrades of the Aprimo software. </span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></div>
